      "content": "While changing demographics can be a factor in market shifts, it is not the only driver of uncertainty in Profile B. Rapidly changing communities often involve broader issues like gentrification pressures, shifting consumer bases, or redevelopment cycles, which all contribute to volatility. The impact of diversity versus infrastructure or schools is complex, but poor infrastructure or declining school quality generally presents a more direct and quantifiable risk to property values than demographic shifts alone.",
